<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Support</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contact.css">
</head>
<body>

<div id="main">

    
    <div id="header">
        <div class="logo">College Dost</div>

        <ul class="navbar">
            <li><a href="/">HOME</a></li>
            <li><a href="/AboutUs">ABOUT</a></li>
            <li><a href="/login" class="btn">LOGIN</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div id="fakeheader"></div>


    <div id="page1">

        <h1>Contact Support</h1>
        <h3>Need help or have any questions?</h3>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>
                We’re here to assist you! If you face any issues while using College Dost or need guidance, feel free to reach out.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>📧 Email: support@collegedost.com</li>
                <li>📍 Location: Department of CSBS, KIT’s College of Engineering, Kolhapur</li>
                <li>🕒 Support Hours: 9:00 AM – 4:30 PM (Tue – Sat)</li>
            </ul>

            <p>You can also use the platform’s chat feature to connect with mentors for quick help.</p>
            <p>We aim to respond to all queries as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>

      
      <form action="/student/contact" method="POST">
         <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>

         <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

         <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>

         <button type="submit">Send Message</button>

           {{#if message}}
             <p style="color:antiquewhite;">{{message}}</p>
           {{/if}}
     </form>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>



